This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to extract information from biomedical text. The use of self-attention mechanism and machine reading comprehension (MRC) techniques suggest that this paper is likely to be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-category. The use of deep learning models and attention mechanisms also suggest that this paper could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification tasks, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category. The use of NLP techniques and machine learning models also suggest that this paper could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks and deep learning models suggest that this paper could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
